Class DistQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars.DistQueue

  • public class DistQueue
extends Object
    A Bounded Priority Queue of DQEntries, where distance is the distance from the testpoint the queue was instantiated with to the star.
    Author:
    cdluo

      • toString2

        public String toString2()
        The same as toString, but omits the first element of the queue. This is used when the user calls KNN with a star name instead of coordinate, since the KNN algorithm will still insert the star itself into the queue. I considered just adding a parameter to toString(), but I decided it would be best for toString to look like every other toString and not take parameters. So I decided to make a new method.
        Returns:
        String
